Access Modifiers

1. public: Accessible from anywhere in the project (class, method, field).

2. default (no keyword, also known as "friendly"): Accessible only within the same package (class, method, field).

3. private: Accessible only within the same class (method, field).

4. protected: Will be explained later; similar to default.

Access Options
1. Access only from within the class.
2. Access only from within the package.
3. Access from anywhere in the project.
